name: The Twisted Watcher - Aron
description:
Before the The Blind Idiot God dreamed of the Universe there was nothing.

And before there was nothing there were monsters, they've been push away to the boundaries of creation but their presence can be seen in the stars like a bright omen.

With these eyes I see.
With these hands I mold.
With this voice I command.
With this mind I think.

I can see everything, I can sense everything, I'm watching and know that I'll always see everything you do.

And enjoy it.
